@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8000

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Create a transfer
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "ACC-12345",
  "toAccount": "ACC-67890",
  "amount": 100.50,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "transfer"
}

### List transactions
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions

### Filter transactions by account and type
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions?accountId=ACC-12345&type=transfer

### Get account balance
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/ACC-12345/balance

### Get account summary
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/ACC-12345/summary

### Calculate simple interest
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/ACC-12345/interest?rate=0.05&days=30

### Export transactions as CSV
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions/export?format=csv
